        "evidence": "<p>The TWIST score is calculated by the addition of the selected points:</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 163.32px; border-width: 1px; border-style: none;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 38.75px;\">\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 66.6667%; height: 38.75px;\"><strong>Variable</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 38.75px;\"><strong>Points</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 44.7968px;\">Testicular swelling</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\">No</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\">Yes</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 44.7968px; width: 33.3333%;\" rowspan=\"2\">Hard testicle</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\">No</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\">Yes</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 22.3984px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.2344px; width: 33.3333%;\" rowspan=\"2\">Absent cremasteric reflex</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 10px;\">No</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 10px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 6.23438px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 6.23438px;\">Yes</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 6.23438px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Nausea/vomiting</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">No</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Yes</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 6.23438px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 6.23438px; width: 33.3333%;\" rowspan=\"2\">High riding testis</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 6.23438px;\">No</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 6.23438px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 6.23438px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 6.23438px;\">Yes</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 6.23438px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
        "facts": "<p>Interpretation:</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 172.187px; border-width: 1px; border-style: none;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 39.3281px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.7314%; height: 39.3281px;\"><strong>TWIST Score</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.505%; height: 39.3281px;\"><strong>Risk of Testicular Torsion</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54.1953px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.7314%; height: 54.1953px;\">0-2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.505%; height: 54.1953px;\">Low, no recommendation for ultrasound</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 39.3281px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.7314%; height: 39.3281px;\">3-4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.505%; height: 39.3281px;\">Intermediate, ultrasound indicated</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 39.3359px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.7314%; height: 39.3359px;\">5-7</td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.505%; height: 39.3359px;\">High, surgical exploration recommended</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
